title: Lower level of private home for rent
posting_body: ['I’m looking for someone to occupy the lower level of my private home.', 'The home is located in South Minneapolis about 5 minutes from Lake Nokomis.', 'The living area has its own privacy wall, separate entrance, and is a 1 bedroom, 1 bath, with comfy living area and tiled dining space.', 'There is a stove and refrigerator in the common area of the lower level as well as a laundry room.', 'Quiet neighborhood with several bus routes, close to major freeways, the U of M and downtown Minneapolis.', 'I’m looking for a mature, relatively quiet person, with a full-time job plus rental and work history.', 'NO smoking.', 'NO pets.', 'Available September 1st.', ' Upon lease signing, I will need first month’s rent and damage deposit of $800.', 'Rent includes laundry, off street parking space, water, gas, garbage and recycling.', 'You are responsible for the electric bill, since the lower level has electric heating and electric stove.', 'We share cable/WIFI ($25).', 'If interested or have any questions, please call', 'show contact info', '.', 'I will set up viewing appointments between 5pm – 7pm on Monday-Friday and Saturday/Sunday by appointment.', 'DO NOT send me email messages.', 'I will NOT respond.', 'Call/Text me to set up a viewing.']
